&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;This position will join the &lt;strong&gt;Advizex &lt;/strong&gt;team, a Myriad360 company.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Advizex:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Advizex, a Myriad360 company, brings together over 50 years of innovation and client commitment. As part of Myriad360’s growing portfolio, Advizex continues to operate with the same trusted expertise and customer-first philosophy—now strengthened by broader resources and reach.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For over 50 years, Advizex has done more than simply keep pace with technology—it has helped organizations stay ahead of it. With deep, real-world experience across healthcare, education, government, manufacturing, &amp;amp; retail, Advizex delivers IT solutions that solve meaningful business challenges across infrastructure, cloud, cybersecurity, automation, and AI.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will join the Advizex team and play a key part in continuing that legacy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Learn more about Advizex &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.advizex.com/&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;
